        "content": "A GP says: 'ESG is fully embedded in our investment process.' The deck shows a policy statement, a carbon slide, DEI language, and a few portfolio-company anecdotes. The immediate allocator question is not whether the materials sound modern. It is whether ESG has changed real decisions: what the GP underwrote, how it priced risk, what it required after close, and whether ownership actions made the business more resilient or more exit-ready."
