        "content": "The GP says: 'The company raised at the same valuation as the prior round, so the mark held up well.' A venture-fluent allocator does not stop there. They ask: Was the round truly flat for common equity, or flat only in headline terms? Was the round led by new external capital, or was it an inside round designed mainly to extend runway and preserve optics?"
