        "content": "The GP says: 'Our venture strategy is differentiated because we have access, judgment, and a strong network in the ecosystem.' It is also not enough for allocator underwriting. A venture-fluent allocator wants to know what edge actually looks like whether the firm's sourcing advantage is real or mostly brand inertia, how decisions are made when evidence is sparse, whether reserve and ownership outcomes validate the process, and whether the edge appears repeatable or just attached to one or two famous wins."
