        "content": "The GP says: \'We focus on senior secured, sponsor-backed direct lending.\' That should not end the underwriting discussion. A production-ready version of this lesson should force the learner to ask what actually repays the loan, how much of leverage depends on adjusted rather than cash EBITDA, what intervention rights the lender really has, how concentrated refinance risk is, and what sponsor behavior typically looks like when a business misses plan."
